divs: Sighting Detailswas out in my backyard late in the night. looking up at the clear sky. I saw a con-trail. I then looked to see what was making the trail and saw a object moving through the sky. at first I thought it was a plane but looking the strobeing was too fast and bright. And it was moving too fast in a west to east direction. I then looked for jet airliners that fly in the area to compare it to, none where around. will be out with a camera at night from now on. Defiantly not a plane, commercial or military that I saw.
